{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9538cfeed6","title":"关于暂时不动富农出租土地问题的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"01b68abbca","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"9538cfeed6"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"3c977b4a28","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"子恢，即邓子恢，当时任中共中央中南局第三书记。"},{"id":"9e85833724","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"激石，即饶激石，当时任中共中央华东局第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b9764fd65f","type":"title","text":"关于暂时不动富农出租土地问题的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6"},{"id":"3c977b4a28","type":"paragraph","text":"子恢同志，并告激石","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6"},{"id":"9e85833724","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿五日电悉。（一）鉴于富农出租地数量不大，暂时不动这点土地影响贫属农所得土地的数量也不会大，现在我的意见仍以为暂时不动较为适宜。（二）但你们可根据你们自己的各项意见起草一个土改法令草案，由子恢同志于五月十五日以后中央开会时带来（子恢同志动身日期另外通知），在中央会议上作最后的讨论和决定。（三）如华东局是赞成暂时不动富农出租土地的，则请华东局起草一个和华中不相同的土改法令草案，以便在中央会议上对照讨论。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6"},{"id":"db629a5c11","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6"},{"id":"8479135546","type":"paragraph","text":"五月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6"}],"page":{"id":"8877410394","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9538cfeed6","start":333,"end":333}}}},"__N_SSG":true}